'''2019年印度洲际杯'''是正式举办以来的第二届赛事，因接受印度英雄摩托公司赞助，又称为'''英雄杯'''或'''英雄洲际杯'''<ref>{{cite web|title=Mumbai Football Arena To Host Hero Intercontinental Cup From June 1|url=https://www.the-aiff.com/news-center-details.htm?id=8928|website=www.the-aiff.com|access-date=13 May 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612145833/https://www.the-aiff.com/news-center-details.htm?id=8928|archive-date=2018-06-12|url-status=dead|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2019年7月7日至19日在[[印度|印度]][[艾哈迈达巴德|艾哈迈达巴德]]举行，由[[印度足协|印度足协]]主办<ref name="aiff statement">{{cite web |title=INDIA TO PLAY SYRIA, TAJIKISTAN & DPR KOREA IN SECOND EDITION OF HERO INTERCONTINENTAL CUP IN JULY |url=https://www.the-aiff.com/news-center-details.htm?id=9667 |website=the-aiff.com |publisher=AIFF |accessdate=13 May 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206104141/https://the-aiff.com/news-center-details.htm?id=9667 |archive-date=2019-12-06 |url-status=dead |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="tajik fed statement">{{cite web |title=TAJIKISTAN NATIONAL TEAM IN THE TOURNAMENT "INTERCONTINENTAL CUP 2019" WILL PLAY WITH SYRIA, THE DPRK AND INDIA |url=http://fft.tj/sbornaya-tadzhikistana-na-turnire-intersontinental-cup-2019-sygraet-s-siriej-kndr-i-indiej/ |website=fft.tj |publisher=Tajikistan Football Association |accessdate=13 May 2019 |archive-date=2019-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520081525/http://fft.tj/sbornaya-tadzhikistana-na-turnire-intersontinental-cup-2019-sygraet-s-siriej-kndr-i-indiej/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="venue">{{cite web |title=HERO INTERCONTINENTAL CUP TO BE HELD IN AHMEDABAD |url=https://www.the-aiff.com/news-center-details.htm?id=9687 |website=the-aiff.com |publisher=AIFF |accessdate=18 May 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521082013/https://the-aiff.com/news-center-details.htm?id=9687 |archive-date=2019-05-21 |url-status=dead |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[朝鲜国家足球队|朝鲜]]在决赛中以1–0战胜[[塔吉克斯坦国家足球队|塔吉克斯坦]]，夺得本届赛事的冠军<ref name="the champion">{{cite web |title=DPR KOREA LIFT HERO INTERCONTINENTAL CUP 2019 TITLE |url=https://www.the-aiff.com/news-center-details.htm?id=9827 |website=the-aiff.com |publisher=AIFF |accessdate=21 July 2019 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20190729145527/https://www.the-aiff.com/news-center-details.htm?id=9827 |archive-date=2019-07-29 |url-status=dead |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

